<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <title>Employer published job applications</title>
  <link rel="shortcut icon" href="images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <link rel="icon" href="images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=0">
  <meta name="description" content='Search result page'/>
  <!-- Stylesheets -->
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'home/flexslider' %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'home/bootstrap.min' %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'home/style' %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'home/responsive' %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'home/jquery.fancybox' %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'home/huan' %>

  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Lato:300i,400,900|Montserrat:400,700" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body class="register-01 employer-published-job-applications  employer-expired-job">
  <div class="wapper">
     <%= render "layouts/header"%>
    <div class="all-jobs">
      <div class="auto-container box-all-jobs">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="breadcrumbs">
                        <ul>
                            <li><a href="#">My jobs</a></li>
                            <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></li>
                            <li><a href="#">Published jobs</a></li>
                            <li><i class="fa fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></li>
                            <li>Front-end Developer</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div><!-- .breadcrumbs -->
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-lg-9 col-md-9 col-sm-9 col-xs-12 item-info">
                            <% @job = Job.find(params[:id])%>
                              <div class="option">
                                <h1 class="title">
                                    <a href="#" title="Front-end Developer"><%= @job[:title]%></a>
                                    <span class="time">
                                        <%= @job[:created_at].strftime("%d %b %Y")%>
                                    </span>
                                </h1>
                              <div class="option-top">

                    <div class="item-note"> 
                      <div class="promotion-flags">
                          <% if @job[:on_the_spot] == "yes" %>
                              <a href="#" class="btn btn-spot waves-effect" title="On The Spot">On The Spot</a>
                          <% end %>
                          <% if @job[:commission] == "yes"%>
                              <a href="#" class="btn btn-commission waves-effect" title="Commission">Commission</a>
                          <% end %>
                      </div><!-- .promotion-flags -->
                    </div>
                    <div class="tag-location">
                      <div class="tag-link">  
                        <a href="#" title="Technology"><%= @job.category_job%></a>
                      </div>
                      <div class="location-link">
                        <a href="#" title="Petaling Jaya"><%=@job.state%></a>
                      </div>
                    </div><!-- .tag-location -->
                                </div><!-- .option top -->
                                <div class="option-bottom">
                                    <div class="row">
                                        <div class="col-lg-9 col-md-9 col-sm-9 col-xs-12">    
                                            <div class="time-work">
                                                <span>Working period: <span class="month">
                                                <% unless @job.working_hour_from.nil?%>
                                                  <%= @job[:working_date_from].try(:strftime, "%B %d at %I:%M%p") %>
                                                <% end %>
                                                     - 
                                                <% unless @job.working_date_to.nil?%>
                                                  <%= @job[:working_date_to].try(:strftime, "%B %d at %I:%M%p")%>
                                                <% end %>

                                                </span></span>
                                                <span>Working Hour: 
                                                    <span class="month">
                                                    <%=@job[:working_hour_from]%> am - <%=@job[:working_hour_to]%> pm
                                                    </span>
                                                </span> 
                                            </div><!-- .time work -->
                                            <div class="time-work">
                                                <span>Language: 
                                                    <span class="font-bold">
                                                        <% if @job[:language_Bahasa_Malaysia] == "1"%>
                                                            Bahasa Malaysia,
                                                        <% end %>
                                                        <% if @job[:language_Chinese] == "1"%>
                                                            Chinese,
                                                        <% end %>
                                                        <% if @job[:language_English] == "1"%>
                                                            English,
                                                        <% end %>
                                                        <% if @job[:language_Cantonese] == "1"%>
                                                            Cantonese,
                                                        <% end %>
                                                        <% if @job[:language_Tamin] == "1"%>
                                                            Tamin,
                                                        <% end %>
                                                        <% if @job[:language_Hokkien] == "1"%>
                                                            Hokkien
                                                        <% end %>
                                                    </span>
                                                </span>
                                            </div><!-- .time work -->

                                            <div class="package-link">

                                                <a href="#">Open to 
                                                <span class="font-bold">
                                                    <%= @job[:availablefor] %>
                                                </span>
                                                </a>

                                                <a href="#"><span class="font-bold">
                                                    <%= @job[:vacancies] %>
                                                </span> vacancies available</a>

                                                <a href="#">Pay 
                                                    <span class="font-bold">
                                                    <%= @job[:payment]%>
                                                    </span>
                                                </a>

                                            </div><!-- .package -->

                                        </div>

                                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 col-xs-12 price">  

                                            <span class="pull-right">RM<%=@job[:salary]%>/<%= @job[:per_day] %> </span>
                                        </div>

                                    </div><!-- .row -->

                                </div><!-- .option bottom -->

              </div><!-- .option -->

                        </div><!-- .item-info -->

                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 col-xs-12 edit">
                            <a class="waves-effect" href="/01-all-jobs-listing/edit-published-job/<%=@job.id%>">Edit</a> 
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-3 col-sm-3 col-xs-12 cancel">
                            <a class="waves-effect" href="/01-all-jobs-listing/cancel-job/<%=@job.id%>">Cancel this job</a> 
                        </div>
                    </div><!-- .row -->

                </div><!-- .container -->

      </div><!-- box-search-result -->



    </div><!-- .All Jobs -->



    <div class="content">

      

      <div class="container">

                <div class="row">

                    <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 job-details">      

                        <div class="panel-group" id="accordion" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">
                        <% @job = Job.find(params[:id])%>
                          <div class="panel panel-default">

                            <div class="panel-heading" role="tab" id="headingOne">

                              <h2 class="panel-title">

                                <a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">

                                  Job Details <span></span>

                                </a>

                              </h2>

                            </div>

                            <div id="collapseOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingOne">

                              <div class="panel-body">

                                <h3>About the Job</h3>
                                    <p><%=@job[:description].html_safe %></p>
                                <h3>Job Requirement</h3>
                                <ul>
                                     <%=@job[:requirements].html_safe %>
                                </ul>
                                <h3>Salary & Benefits</h3>
                                <ul>
                                    <%= @job[:benefits].html_safe%>
                                </ul>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </div><!-- .panel group -->
                    </div><!-- .job details -->
                </div><!-- .row -->
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-8 col-sm-8 col-xs-12 application">      
            <!-- Nav tabs -->
            <ul class="nav nav-tabs" role="tablist">
              <li role="presentation" class="active">
                <a href="#tab-application" aria-controls="application" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Application 
                  <span>(<%= Applied.where(status_job: "applied", job_id: params[:id], employer_id: User.find(session[:user_id]).id).count%></span>)
                </a>
              </li>
              <li role="presentation">
                  <a href="#tab-awarded" aria-controls="Awarded" role="tab" data-toggle="tab">Awarded <span>(<%= Applied.where(status_job: "awarded", job_id: params[:id], employer_id: User.find(session[:user_id]).id).count%></span>)
                  </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <!-- Tab panes -->
            <div class="tab-content">
              <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane active" id="tab-application">
                <ul class="application-list">
                  <% if $load_more_job.blank? %>
                    <% default_job = 10%>
                  <% else %>
                    <% default_job = $load_more_job%>
                  <% end %>
                  <% Applied.where(job_id: params[:id], status_job: "applied").limit(default_job).each do |job| %>
                  <% parttimer= User.find(job[:parttimer_id]) %>
                    <li>
                      <div class="avatar">
                        <%= image_tag parttimer.avatar.url("medium"), alt: "Avata",:class => 'avatar-apply-job'%>
                      </div>
                      <div class="info">
                        <h4>
                          <a class="fancybox" href="/01-all-jobs-listing/published-job/full-profile-parttimer/<%=parttimer.id%>">
                            <%= parttimer[:full_name]%>
                          </a>
                        </h4>
                        <% unless parttimer[:preferred_working_location1].blank?%>
                        <div class="location-link">
                          <a href="#" title="Petaling Jaya">
                            <%= parttimer[:preferred_working_location1]%>
                          </a>
                        </div>
                        <% end %>
                      </div>
                      <div class="award">
                        <%= link_to "Award", {controller: "home", action: "awarded_job_for_parttimer", id: job.id }, class: "waves-effect" %>
                      </div>
                    </li>
                  <% end %>
                </ul>
              </div><!-- .tab application -->
              <div role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane" id="tab-awarded">
                <ul class="application-list">
                  <% Applied.where(job_id: @job.id, status_job: "awarded").all.each do |job| %>
                  <% @parttimer= User.find(job[:parttimer_id]) %>
                    <li>
                      <div class="avatar">
                        <%= image_tag @parttimer.avatar.url("medium"), alt: "Avata",:class => 'avatar-apply-job'%>
                      </div>
                      <div class="info">
                        <h4>
                        <a class="fancybox" href="/01-all-jobs-listing/published-job/full-profile-parttimer/<%=@parttimer.id%>">
                          <%= @parttimer[:full_name]%>
                        </a>
                        </h4>
                        <div class="location-link">
                          <a href="#" title="Petaling Jaya"><%= @parttimer[:preferred_working_location1]%>
                          </a>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      <div class="awarded">
                        <a class="waves-effect" href="#">Awarded</a>
                      </div>
                    </li>
                  <% end %>
                </ul>
              </div><!-- .tab-awarded -->
            </div><!-- .tab content -->
            <div class="load-more">
             <!--  <a class="waves-effect" title="Load More" href="/01-all-jobs-listing/published-job/<%=@job.id%>?page=1">Load More</a> -->
               <%= link_to "Load More", {controller: "home", action: "load_more", id: default_job }, :class=> "waves-effect" %>
            </div>
          </div><!-- .application -->
        </div><!-- .row -->
      </div><!-- .container -->
    </div><!-- .content -->
    <%= render "layouts/footer"%>
  </div><!-- wapper -->
    <% unless @parttimer.nil?%>
      <div id="inline1" style="display: none;">
          <div class="profile-popup">
            <div class="popup-content">
              <div class="popup-image">
                <%= image_tag "popup-image.png", alt: "popup image"%>
              </div>
              <div class="popup-info">
                <h4>Full Name </h4>
                <span> <%= @parttimer[:preferred_working_location1]%> </span>
                <span>Member since <%= @parttimer[:created_at].strftime("%d %B %Y")%></span>
              </div>
              <div class="jobs-available">
                <span>10</span>
                <h5>Completed</h5>
                <h5>Jobs</h5>
              </div>
              <p>We need a web design for it, preferred web design style and pattern is Kickstarter(please try to sign up an account and see how their membe, clean, simple and sleek yet informative. This is how Part-time Bee's logo looks like…</p>
              <div class="btn-popup">
                <a href="/01-all-jobs-listing/published-job/full-profile-parttimer/<%=@parttimer[:id]%>">See Full Profile</a>
              </div>
            </div><!-- .popup body-->
        </div><!-- .popup -->
      </div>
    <% end %>
<%= javascript_include_tag "home/jquery" %>
<%= javascript_include_tag "home/bootstrap.min" %>
<%= javascript_include_tag "home/jquery.flexslider" %>
<%= javascript_include_tag "home/parttimebee-custom" %>
<%= javascript_include_tag "home/ware" %>
<%= javascript_include_tag "home/jquery.fancybox" %>
<%= javascript_include_tag "home/parallax" %>
<script type="text/javascript">
  $("a.fancybox").click(function(){
    $.ajax({
      url:'http://parttimebee.my/01-all-jobs-listing/published-job/1?game=online',
      type:'get',
      dataType:'html',
      processData:false
    });
  });

  function getUrlParameter(sParam) {
      var sPageURL = decodeURIComponent(window.location.search.substring(1)),
          sURLVariables = sPageURL.split('&'),
          sParameterName,
          i;
      for (i = 0; i < sURLVariables.length; i++) {
          sParameterName = sURLVariables[i].split('=');

          if (sParameterName[0] === sParam) {
              return sParameterName[1] === undefined ? true : sParameterName[1];
          }
      }
  };
</script>
<script>
    jQuery(document).ready(function() {
          jQuery('.fancybox').fancybox();
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>